Package edu.udel.cis.taschd.gen

The course module provides classes for representing the generator of assignments of courses to course assistants.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Assign
    The Hungarian class is responsible for optimizing and making assignments between Sections and CA based on the score provided.
    GenerateAssignment
    The GenerateAssignment represents a generator tool for a CourseAssistantPool and a CourseInstancePool.
    Hungarian
    Solve an n-by-n assignment problem.
    ScoreTable
    Represents a generator tool for a CourseAssistantPool and a set of CourseInstancePools.
    TableInstance
    TableInstance is an object for storing information for a ScoreTable Each store table will store the information of CourseAssistant CourseInstance Section and rows and columns in the ScoreTable By using this table, we can quick access result in ScoreTable for example: ScoreTable will give a final result of indexes.
